    <item>
      <title>乔治·桑托斯认罪，承认滥用竞选资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/george-santos-pleads-guilty-admits-misusing-campaign-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前众议员乔治桑托斯在竞选国会议员期间谎称自己曾在高盛集团和花旗集团工作，最终他承认在竞选国会议员期间犯有电信欺诈和身份盗窃罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/george-santos-pleads-guilty-admits-misusing-campaign-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 19:54:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
